  <name>ProPad</name>
  <summary>A modern, safe, and adaptive markdown editor with rich formatting and multi-device sync</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      ProPad is a modern, user-friendly, and adaptive markdown editor built with GTK 4 and Libadwaita.
      It provides a clean interface for writing and editing markdown with rich formatting capabilities.
      With synchronized scrolling, you can seamlessly view and edit your markdown content.
      It has support for Mermaid and LaTeX with GitHub alert tags support in markdown with preview.
      The application is designed to be safe and secure, with a focus on data integrity.
    </p>
    <p>Advanced features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean and intuitive interface following GNOME HIG</li>
      <li>Rich text formatting with toolbar</li>
      <li>File manager for organizing documents</li>
      <li>Search and replace functionality</li>
      <li>Export to multiple formats</li>
      <li>Dark mode support</li>
      <li>Auto-save functionality</li>
      <li>GPU-accelerated rendering for smooth performance</li>
      <li>Synchronized scrolling in preview modes</li>
      <li>File history tracking and versioning</li>
      <li>Support for tables, Mermaid diagrams, LaTeX math, and GitHub alerts</li>
      
    </ul>
    <p>
      Whether you're taking notes, writing documentation, or editing markdown files,
      ProPad provides all the tools you need in a distraction-free and highly capable environment.
    </p>
  </description>

